<p>The <code>&lt;figure&gt;</code> + <code>&lt;figcaption&gt;</code> pattern is the recommended way to add visible attribution to a blockquote, with the <code>&lt;cite&gt;</code> element wrapping the work title inside the caption.</p>

<h2>Edit Documentation</h2>
<p>On <code>&lt;del&gt;</code> and <code>&lt;ins&gt;</code>, the <code>cite</code> attribute points to a changelog, ticket, or document explaining why the edit was made. Pair it with <a href="/docs/attributes/datetime/"><code>datetime</code></a> for a complete edit record.</p>

